}

###

# @name createMechanic
POST {{baseUrl}}/employees/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Carlos Mecanico",
  "documentType": 0,
  "document": "27182818205",
  "email": "carlos.mecanico@garageflow.com",
  "phoneNumber": "11933334444",
